ActNational Capital Act
SubjectNational Capital Commission ** Granting Renewal - 7772092 Canada Inc. **
PrecisOrder Authorizing the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION to grant the option to extend for five years, commencing on April 1, 2016, the existing five-year lease with 7772092 CANADA INC. in order to operate a take-out restaurant on the premises being a portion of the ground floor located at 96-100 Sparks Street in Ottawa.
